  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Wow, it looks like the heroes managed to reach the last room! But don\u2019t
    worry, you still have an ace up your sleeve: the boss! When heroes reach the
    last room, SMOL will be able to use his power to possess a powerful creature
    to fend off the last of the heroes.  \r\n\r\nWhen the boss phase starts, SMOL
    will automatically possess the boss selected at the beginning of the run and
    can control it during the fight. You will be able to use different actions to
    fight and defeat the heroes to win the day and survive even longer. Every boss
    has different actions, so choose your favorite! \r\n\r\nTo use the main boss
    action, press LEFT CLICK, just like how you control other monsters in the dungeon.
    \r\n\r\nTo use the two secondary actions of the bosses, press the Q and E keys.
    \r\n\r\nThe fight ends when one of two conditions is accomplished: either the
    heroes are defeated, and you can start the second day, or the boss is defeated,
    and it's game over! "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: d64da69360c2c66489c9deeb5f1c79c7, type: 2}
